<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
.container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
.header { border-bottom: 2px solid #1565C0; padding-bottom: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.title { color: #1565C0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }
.info-box { background: #f5f7fa; border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 16px 0; }
.footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 12px; }
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header"><div class="title">SurgicalHub — Facture</div></div>

  <p>Veuillez trouver ci-joint la facture <strong>{{ invoice.number ?? invoice.id }}</strong> pour la firme <strong>{{ invoice.firm.name }}</strong>.</p>

  <div class="info-box">
    <strong>Période :</strong> {{ invoice.periodStart|date('d/m/Y') }} → {{ invoice.periodEnd|date('d/m/Y') }}<br>
    <strong>Montant total HTVA :</strong> {{ invoice.totalAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €<br>
    <strong>Lignes :</strong> {{ invoice.lines|length }}
  </div>

  <p>Ce document est joint à cet email au format PDF.</p>

  <div class="footer">SurgicalHub — document confidentiel</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
